Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.13,0:01:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.14,0:02:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十一話\N傳達不到的相思\N劍心的出發旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.95,0:02:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.28,0:02:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天太晚睡了 再讓我睡一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.12,0:02:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起床了懶鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還有心情睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道今天是什麼日子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.86,0:02:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是五月十四日\N是大久保大人要來的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 是大久保這個混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.27,0:02:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.60,0:02:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 我們去找劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 就是今天嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論大久保大人 如何給他壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.36,0:03:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都會支持他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.79,0:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心的意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他什麼也沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不對爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.21,0:03:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚這裏有螢火蟲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,螢火蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一閃一閃好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初夏的螢火蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.62,0:03:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年會是溫暖的一年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了這個季節 螢火蟲就會出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心沒看過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.89,0:03:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 劍心來這裏還不到一年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但好像已住了好久似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.60,0:03:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕不讓劍心離開\N我要他一直住在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次帶劍心看螢火蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.88,0:03:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們今晚去抓螢火蟲 好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,螢火蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定哦劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我.. 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.76,0:04:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還有心情在這裏散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.10,0:04:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可不可正經點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心這個人就是心腸太軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.74,0:04:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們絕不會讓你受人擺佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.21,0:04:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別被大久保那混蛋\N美麗的謊言給騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你好像很討厭政府官員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.79,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果大久保 是自私自利的政客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.39,0:04:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤就不會甘心幫他做事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個壞蛋警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.73,0:04:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我們聯手 才有真正的正義存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.41,0:04:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤是個 充滿正義感的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使到了明治時代 他仍然沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.15,0:05:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立誓要消滅黑暗中的邪惡力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實他是個值得交的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.39,0:05:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.06,0:05:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們討厭他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 藤田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.90,0:05:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼新撰組的成員\N總是做出令人討厭的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.68,0:05:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道緋村決定了沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.29,0:05:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定去找大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.43,0:05:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 他不是要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.23,0:05:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保大人是個忙碌的人\N還是我去比較快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.41,0:06:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.78,0:06:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你一定要去的話\N我就給你喝下這個迷藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.32,0:06:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你全身動不了 你就哪也去不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無聊的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.93,0:06:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠 你什麼時候學會這個玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.17,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的獨家秘方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是決定去一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.94,0:06:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道大久保住哪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已去向地方官打聽過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.88,0:06:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了紀尾井山邊就可以找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.82,0:06:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 你會愈幫愈忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.50,0:07:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.51,0:07:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心已在神谷道場住習慣了\N不會隨便離開我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.04,0:07:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他該不會答應大久保吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.18,0:07:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會讓他去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心去哪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他什麼時候回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.06,0:07:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.27,0:07:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的就能帶給國家和平 人民幸福嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.80,0:07:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的會議真冗長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.57,0:08:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是被內務省雜事給擔擱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.04,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到了緋村的住處 都已天黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道緋村決定如何了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 一定要說服他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果緋村不願意來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個國家就要滅亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心別人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔心你自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的命快不保了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄叫我告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.04,0:08:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別大費周章想叫緋村劍心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.01,0:08:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本 以後交給他接管就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是石川縣士族 島田一良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是長連豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奸賊大久保快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車伕解決了大家快上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人捷足先登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.38,0:09:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經向報社發佈暗殺令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就當做是我們殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.49,0:09:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正也沒人看見 就說大久保是我們殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.80,0:09:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保卿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.15,0:10:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不想有此下場 你就少管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,號外號外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.82,0:10:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保內務大人被暗殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.16,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在紀尾井山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的精神領袖被刺殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.30,0:11:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是對政府不滿的石川縣士族干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.05,0:11:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是志志雄的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.72,0:11:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他早就得知有人要刺殺大人\N他利用他們殺掉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.36,0:11:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己卻不用出面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.93,0:11:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後藉此分化人心\N再慢慢瓦解政府力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是福島縣的山吉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是最後見到\N大久保大人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.95,0:11:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於要趕回東京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天清晨特別提早\N到官邸去面見大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.49,0:11:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到卻發生這樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.83,0:11:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治維新雖然已過了十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.26,0:12:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但推動的情形\N卻不如預想中的順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.84,0:12:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穩固國家基礎\N最少需要三十年的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.08,0:12:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個十年是創業期\N第二個十年是發展期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.92,0:12:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是安定國家最重要的時期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.15,0:12:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此才能完完全全\N成為一個理想的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何謂理想的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是民主國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民主國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.53,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是由人民統治的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.37,0:12:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是從古至今\N日本一直在努力完成的大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.91,0:12:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為民主國家之時\N也就是維新成功之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.05,0:12:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個理想也太大了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.66,0:13:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要大久保健在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人不解的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.20,0:13:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平常沉默的大人\N今早卻異常熱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.88,0:13:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與我大談他的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎已預料到\N自己將遭預不測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.35,0:13:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許他想為國家\N盡自己最後的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川路好像十分悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.73,0:13:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他對大久保大人非常忠貞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過不只川路該傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.54,0:13:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去了大久保大人\N也是國家的損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.18,0:13:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不久後 政局一定會開始大亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.52,0:14:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄也一定會趁機攪亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.56,0:14:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤 你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一條路 回到京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解決志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.81,0:14:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,號外大久保大人被暗殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會有大事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會又發生戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府說不定會完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新就此結束了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政局又要開始混亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再也不想再回到那個時代了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.40,0:14:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世間再也沒有正義可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.44,0:14:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成民主國家就是維新成功之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.51,0:15:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要大久保健在 理想一定會成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.78,0:15:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不久後 政局一定會開始大亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.45,0:15:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄也一定會趁機攪亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無能的政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.12,0:15:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我寧可被處死 也不要劍心去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.16,0:15:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心去殺志志雄會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.37,0:15:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心已不再殺人了\N我們絕不讓他去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.94,0:15:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,江山易改本性難移 武士就是武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.75,0:15:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到死都不會變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.19,0:15:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你一生 都無法改變的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.27,0:15:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沾了血的雙手 豈能輕易放下屠刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.81,0:16:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武士到死都是武士 拔刀齊才是真正的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在決鬥中求生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.65,0:16:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時代已開始變動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.66,0:16:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能再躲起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.68,0:16:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼晚還有人要看病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺快回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會趕回來見劍心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.99,0:16:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我送你到停車場吧\N這麼晚了一個女孩子不安全的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.64,0:17:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心回來我會通知你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道劍心在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.72,0:17:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心就不必去京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去找他看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.56,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮的螢火蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.62,0:18:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.42,0:18:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保今早被暗殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.76,0:18:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是志志雄派人幹的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.86,0:18:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能再任他為非做歹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定要去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.11,0:18:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又要回去做武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.58,0:18:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.82,0:19:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這十年來 我一直要讓自己 忘記是個武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.76,0:19:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我知道我的身體裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.83,0:19:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是流著武士的血液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.64,0:19:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你曾告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.37,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何你都不會再殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.01,0:19:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是劍心 不是武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.08,0:19:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我也曾說過 只要大家有危難時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.25,0:19:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是會再拿起武士刀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.27,0:19:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次遇見你時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.07,0:19:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你告訴我 不在乎我的過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.57,0:19:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日子久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.92,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我甚至忘記 自己曾是劍客的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是流浪人 我會再回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.79,0:21:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治十一年五月十四日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.29,0:21:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心決心重回江湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失於漆黑的夜色中

